        p1="Three UK voice assistants: Alexa (45%), Google Assistant (30%), Siri (15%). Alexa setup: Alexa app > Devices > assign to room. Name devices clearly (Living Room Lamp, not Lamp 1). Enable skills for each brand. Google setup: Google Home > Add > assign to room. Use Matter for seamless setup. Apple Home setup: Home app > Add Accessory > scan HomeKit/Matter code. Voice profiles: Alexa recognises voices for personalised responses. Google Voice Match enables personalised voice unlock. Siri recognises different voices on HomePod.",
