        p1="Three main multi-room platforms for UK homes: Amazon Multi-Room Music - group Echo devices in Alexa app. Supports Amazon Music, Spotify, Apple Music, Tidal. Group by room name (Kitchen + Living Room). Google Speaker Groups - group Nest/Chromecast devices in Google Home app. Supports YouTube Music, Spotify, Apple Music. Apple AirPlay 2 - works across HomePods and compatible speakers (Sonos, Denon, Bowers & Wilkins). All three support synchronised playback with near-zero latency. For a dedicated multi-room system, Sonos is the premium choice - Sonos Era 100 (£249), Sonos Era 300 (£449), Sonos Port (£449) for existing speakers. Sonos works with all three voice platforms via Alexa, Google, or Siri.",
