        h1="Camera Integration with Smart Home Platforms",
        p1="Security cameras enhance smart home security when integrated with your platform. Ring cameras integrate with Alexa - view live feed on Echo Show, receive motion alerts, trigger routines (lights on when camera detects motion). Integration requires Ring skill in Alexa. Eufy cameras work with both Alexa and Google - view via smart displays, receive notifications. No subscription needed for local storage. Hive cameras integrate within Hive ecosystem - camera, alarm, heating, lights all in one app. Arlo cameras integrate with Alexa, Google, and Apple HomeKit - rich notifications, smart display viewing, routine triggers. All platforms support: motion-triggered recording, push notifications, smart display live view, and routine integration. Camera feeds appear on Echo Show and Nest Hub when doorbell is pressed.",
