        fq=[("Does vacation mode save energy?","Yes - setting thermostat to 12-15C saves £50-£150 on a 2-week holiday compared to keeping normal schedule. Turning off appliances saves additional £10-£30."),("How do I simulate occupancy realistically?","Use Alexa Hunches for automatic scheduling. Create routines with random on/off times at 15-45 minute intervals. Vary the pattern daily - have lights on in different rooms each evening."),("What if there is a water leak while I am away?","Water leak sensors near appliances send urgent notifications. If you have a motorised shut-off valve (like Tado Flood Free), it automatically shuts off the main water supply. Otherwise, call a neighbour or keyholder immediately.")],
